title: TEMU
text: I was a little iffy to try the app at first considering what I had heard about it. I enjoy making miniatures and the arts and crafts bargains were just too good to be true. I am very impressed by the quality of the items that I have received. I usually get the items a week earlier than I am anticipating them to come. Sometimes the boxes can come a little squished but I don‚Äôt mind since they are not gifts and the contents inside are perfectly fine. They have great sales that I usually take advantage of. There are ways to get extra items by sending requests to people you know which I have not done. There are little games that can get you extra items or deals but I have not really looked into those since I don‚Äôt have time. The regular sales are definitely great enough. I do get a lot of texts and emails. I don‚Äôt like to ship but I do find this the absolutely funnest way to quickly shop and get art and craft items.
